01:07:20.119 --> 01:07:23.054
would be one way,
one function of the light,

01:07:23.054 --> 01:07:25.550
the like the light,
the light of the mind,

01:07:25.550 --> 01:07:27.400
the light of the sun,
whatever.

01:07:27.400 --> 01:07:29.652
Because of that,
the artificial light,

01:07:29.652 --> 01:07:33.246
but there is a way in which
Dante is now thinking about what

01:07:33.246 --> 01:07:35.380
is called metaphysics of light.
 

01:07:35.380 --> 01:07:37.550
What is the light in and of
itself?

01:07:37.550 --> 01:07:40.222
The light--Dante by the way,
if you really want to know

01:07:40.222 --> 01:07:42.045
this,
Dante distinguishes between the

01:07:42.045 --> 01:07:43.840
