01:07:45.581 --> 01:07:49.349
and so on light,
lamp and so on and a number of

01:07:49.349 --> 01:07:51.340
scientific distinctions.
 

01:07:51.340 --> 01:07:56.820
Here he is talking about the
vision of the origin of light,

01:07:56.820 --> 01:08:01.050
"In thy light we see the
light," that's the meaning

01:08:01.050 --> 01:08:02.179
of the phrase.
 

